'''海丰莕菜'''（[[學名|學名]]：{{lang|la|''Limnanthemum coronatum'' Dunn}}）[[莕菜属|莕菜属]][[水生植物|水生植物]]，极度濒危种。其花直径約{{convert|3|mm}}，黄色，长花柱呈开裂状。约1912年在中国发现，随后植物界再无相关发现资料。由于一直未发现活体及[[标本|标本]]，将其列入疑似种。<ref>{{cite news|title=Limnanthemum coronatum Dunn|url=http://www.tropicos.org/Name/50002473|accessdate=2014-11-08|newspaper=tropicos|archive-date=2018-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180711185735/http://www.tropicos.org/Name/50002473|dead-url=no}}</ref>直至2013年12月，[[武汉植物园|武汉植物园]]科研人员[[肖克炎|肖克炎]]采集到一种莕菜属未知植物标本，经研究确认为海丰莕菜，并将结果发表在国际植物分类学期刊《[[Phytotaxa|Phytotaxa]]》上后正式确认并发表。<ref>{{cite news|author=Yadong Zhou, Keyan Xiao, Guangwan Hu, Qinghua Zhan, Qingfeng Wang|title=Reappraisal of Nymphoides coronata (Menyanthaceae), A 100-year-lost Species Endemic to South China|url=http://biotaxa.org/Phytotaxa/article/view/phytotaxa.184.3.8|accessdate=2014-11-08|newspaper=Phytotaxa|year=2014|volume=184|pages=1179-3155|archive-date=2020-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200519135306/https://www.biotaxa.org/Phytotaxa/article/view/phytotaxa.184.3.8|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://facstaff.uww.edu/tipperyn/Meny-taxonomy/Naur.htm |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-02-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150226131800/http://facstaff.uww.edu/tipperyn/Meny-taxonomy/Naur.htm |archivedate=2015-02-26 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cas.cn/ky/kyjz/201411/t20141106_4248145.shtml |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-02-26 |archive-date=2020-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200405145800/http://www.cas.cn/ky/kyjz/201411/t20141106_4248145.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

